                            The session.executionRootDirectory variable is flagged as an error in IntelliJ.
                            To hide the false error, just add it as a Maven property in Preference->Maven->Runner
                        -->
                        <rulesUri>file:///${session.executionRootDirectory}/maven-version-rules.xml</rulesUri>
                    </configuration>
                </plugin>
